* Create Row\nFilter Policies
** Purpose
***_ Control which rows users see
***_ Based on governed tags
** UDF
***_ Returns BOOLEAN
***_ TRUE = row visible
***_ FALSE = row hidden
** CREATE POLICY syntax
***_ ON CATALOG / SCHEMA
***_ ROW FILTER <function>
***_ TO <principal>
***_ MATCH COLUMNS hasTagValue(...)
** Catalog Explorer
***_ Visual policy creation
***_ Policies tab on catalog/schema
** Applies to
***_ Tables matching tag criteria
***_ Automatically for new matching tables
@endmindmap
